{"id":259083,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/奇闻录-蜗居人家/","date":"2012-10-25T07:46:25Z","modified":"2012-10-25T07:46:25Z","title":"奇闻录 | 蜗居人家","content":"<p><p>贵阳市岳英街口，妈妈马竹珍和6岁的儿子马振杰蜗居在一个狭窄的房间内。因为没有房子，妈妈利用起岳英街38号楼的一个缝隙居住，这个缝隙纵深约三四米，高约一米，最宽处也只一米多，整个缝隙不规则。<span></span></p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\t\t\t<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/wojurenjia/900x600_8elvhvgg00ap0001.jpg\" title=\"10月23日，贵阳市岳英街口，年仅6岁的马振杰小朋友常常被妈妈关在家里，他只得从这个风口看外面。\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img title=\"贵阳母子蜗居楼旁缝隙 房屋宽1米1\" alt=\"贵阳母子蜗居楼旁缝隙 房屋宽1米1\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/wojurenjia/thumbs/thumbs_900x600_8elvhvgg00ap0001.jpg\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\t\t</div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\t\t\t<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/wojurenjia/900x600_8elvi0l700ap0001.jpg\" title=\"10月23日，贵阳市岳英街口，年仅6岁的马振杰小朋友猫着腰跟着妈妈从家里走出来。有市民称这是最牛的蜗居人家。\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img title=\"贵阳母子蜗居楼旁缝隙 房屋宽1米2\" alt=\"贵阳母子蜗居楼旁缝隙 房屋宽1米2\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/wojurenjia/thumbs/thumbs_900x600_8elvi0l700ap0001.jpg\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\t\t</div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\t\t\t<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/wojurenjia/900x600_8elvi1cq00ap0001.jpg\" title=\"一米一左右高的马振杰小朋友进出家只能靠爬，由于房间狭窄，整个地面都是杂物。图为10月23日，马振杰在他的家里展示妈妈的照片。\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img title=\"贵阳母子蜗居楼旁缝隙 房屋宽1米3\" alt=\"贵阳母子蜗居楼旁缝隙 房屋宽1米3\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/wojurenjia/thumbs/thumbs_900x600_8elvi1cq00ap0001.jpg\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\t\t</div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\t\t\t<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/wojurenjia/900x600_8elvhu4q00ap0001.jpg\" title=\"马竹珍摆摊为生。\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img title=\"贵阳母子蜗居楼旁缝隙 房屋宽1米4\" alt=\"贵阳母子蜗居楼旁缝隙 房屋宽1米4\" src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/gallery/wojurenjia/thumbs/thumbs_900x600_8elvhu4q00ap0001.jpg\" width=\"170\" height=\"128\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\t\t</div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\t\t